data.description:
Three bedroom, two bath single family block home with metal roof was updated in 2015 and 2022. The garge was converted into and 16 x 14ft bedroom and the 9 x 14ft bedroom was converted into an office with W/D storage. Double pane windows, bathroom fixtures, new septic tank and drainfield, and water well pump and tank were all installed in 2022. House has central heat and air via a heat-pump 2016, R-30 attic insulation, all electric appliances, whole house attic fan in ceiling, ceiling fans, and ceramic tile flooring for easy care. Combined living room and dining room with step saver kitchen, front porch with windows and a small open back porch. Washer and dryer, heat pump, and newer hot water heater are located in attached storage room. Additional amenities include:
*Large garden plot

*8 x 20 wired storage building with a 8x20 overhang
*8 x 8 block sheds with two attached 8 x 8 overhangs
*Water well, pump and tank replaced 2022
*Fenced around perimeter with drive-thru entrance gate
data.whatILove: The quiet rural setting located just 2-3 miles from  Ichetucknee Springs State Park with ample space from an organic farm or small animals. The recent updates make is move-in ready just needing your personal touch.
